REQUIRE PYTHON 3.3+

1)install latest python
========================
$ wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.4.2/Python-3.4.2.tgz --no-check-certificate
$ tar zxvf Python-3.4.2.tgz
$ cd Python-3.4.2
$ ./configure --enable-shared
$ make
$ make install
$ echo "/usr/local/lib" | sudo tee /etc/ld.so.conf
$ /sbin/ldconfig 

2)install netifaces
===================
$ pip3.4 install netifaces

3)install the lib
================
$ cd lispy
$ python3.4 setup.py install



this also install this pylig script
usage: $ python3.4 pylig.py <map-resolver> <destination-eid>
